    {
      "role": "user",
      "content": "I mean, I hear that, but it feels like there's a lot of pushback on some of those ideas in certain parts of society and in some medical circles. When you say \"the scientific consensus\" and \"growing acceptance,\" are you saying those debates are basically over and it's just a settled fact now? Or is there still real disagreement on the actual science behind it?",
